I left India 24 years ago, but Punjab remains in me. I got very emotional listening to this Jugni. these songs keep me alive and connected to my beautiful Punjabi culture. 
🥲 "Raavi ton chnaab puchda ki hal a satluj da"  

"Wahga boder ty rah puchdi lahoran dy"❤‍🩹🥲

Jeonda wasde rahoon legend Gurdas Maan & Diljit Dosanjh.
